          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: Hymns in commemoration of the blessed Virgin, the Saints (such as Abbā Bīshōi, Bar-saumā, etc.), and the Dead, arranged according to the tones; Theophilus of Alexandria. Discourse of Theophilus of Alexandria; Isaac of Antioch. Discourse of Isaac of Antioch; Mār George. A prayer of Mār George (?); Hymns and prayers for the principal canonical hours of the ferial days, viz. ܢܓܗܐ, ܠܠܝܐ, and ܨܦܪܐ. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 11 items.</note>
